comments:
Build ID: M20060921-0945

Steps To Reproduce:
1. Create a class like the one below.
2. Press Ctrl+Space in between the <>. An error appears.
3. Click OK twice to get the error messages away :-)


Sample class:

import java.util.List;

public class GenericVarargs {
	// press Ctrl+Space between the <> in next line
	public void foo(List<>... bla) {}
}
